# Component Guidelines

## Structure
Each section of the page is its own component file:
- `Header.tsx` – sticky nav, mobile hamburger
- `Hero.tsx` – centered headline + subtext
- `About.tsx` – Über uns section
- `Services.tsx` – Tätigkeitsfelder with 3 cards
- `Structure.tsx` – Struktur bullet points
- `Contact.tsx` – Address + contact form
- `Footer.tsx` – Copyright line

## When Adding New Sections
1. Create component in `src/components/`
2. Use same spacing pattern: `px-6 py-28`, inner `mx-auto max-w-[1100px]`
3. Section title: `text-[13px] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-[#f97627]`
4. Add `id` attribute for anchor nav scrolling
5. Add corresponding nav link in `Header.tsx`
6. Import and add to `App.tsx` in correct order

## shadcn/ui Usage
- Add new components via `npx shadcn@latest add [component]`
- Never modify files in `src/components/ui/` directly
- Compose shadcn primitives in custom components
